originalText.text: This is a terribly unreliable, unprofessional, and irresponsible service. I booked a service for deep-cleaning because my regular cleaning lady is on vacation for a month and I am doing an apartment swap with someone in Europe. Someone was supposed to come today between 12 and 2. I rushed from work to be there. No one came. I called at 2:30. They told me the person was in traffic and will arrive within 20 minutes. I call again at 3:30 pm. They put me on hold for 30 minutes and hang up on me. I call again and they tell me the person is at the hospital and no one will come. I have a plane early tomorrow morning and I have now been cleaning like crazy for hours and I have a few more hours to go.
